title: Busta Rhymes Q-Tip - The Abstract And The Dragon (2013) (Full Mixtape) (+download) (New)
description: What we have here is a brotherhood. A friendship that extends past music, but also has an extensive musical history. The Abstract & The Dragon is more-so a compilation of their work over the years with new records sprinkled in. Another cool aspect about the mixtape is that both also add verses to classic records like Busta hops on A Tribe Called Quest's "God Lives Through." It's a great example of what a mixtape represents.
